# The Darcs library

Darcs is available as a Haskell library, but it is very much a work in
progress. We currently lack a stable API, but we hope to develop one in
the future.

# Potential uses

-  [Graphical user interface](GraphicalInterface)
-  Dependency visualiser
-  Branch visualiser -
   [issue1200](http://bugs.darcs.net/issue1200)
-  Line range change viewer -
   [issue1445](http://bugs.darcs.net/issue1445)
-  Fancy darcs replace -
   [issue887](http://bugs.darcs.net/issue887)

